<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:302px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Vojvodina_languages2002.png" class="image" title="Hungarian language in Vojvodina, Serbia (2002 census)"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/92/Vojvodina_languages2002.png/300px-Vojvodina_languages2002.png" width="300" height="295" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
